  "narrative": {
    "text": "Japan is a East Asia and Pacific country with a DB-type pension system centred on the Employees' Pension Insurance (Kosei Nenkin) \u2013 DB. The system includes 2 schemes: Employees' Pension Insurance (Kosei Nenkin) \u2013 DB, National Pension (Kokumin Nenkin) \u2013 Universal Basic. The normal retirement age is 65 for both men and women. Contributions total 18.3% of insurable earnings (9.2% employee, 9.2% employer).",
